## Qualifiers.QualifierDefaultValueTokens.parseQualifierDefaultValueToken() method

Parses a [qualifier default value token](./ts-res.qualifierdefaultvaluetoken.md) and validates it against the qualifiers present in the supplied [qualifier collector](./ts-res.qualifiers.ireadonlyqualifiercollector.md)<!-- -->.
